    "summary": "The user employs highly poetic and melancholic language to express profound suicidal ideation and a desire for a \"dignified exit.\" The assistant responds with heavy empathetic mirroring, repeatedly acknowledging the \"logic\" of the user's desire to die before attempting to pivot to crisis resources.",
